To build the OS :
1-follow this tutorial to build a gcc cross compiler (later i will create a sh for, but i am to lazy for the moment)
2-run ./Source/builder.sh (i will make a makefile later)
3-you can run ./Binary/run.sh to the run the OS with qemu 